ņThis seat is dedicated to the memory of my
Dear Wife Johanna.
She loved these gardens and died on 21/7/94
Albert Divell

In Loving Memory Of Albert Divell 1911-2002
Husband of Johanna
He Loved Life And London
From All His Family"“
